description:
Haisaki Shinme was the Warden of http://anidb.net/ch95846 [Cochlea]. After his predecessor, http://anidb.net/ch74211 [Misaka Kyouji], died during http://anidb.net/ch70052 [Aogiri Tree]`s attack on Cochlea, he was promoted from Deputy Warden to Warden. Formerly, he was an interrogator. He was killed during the Third Cochlea Raid.
Source: Tokyo Ghoul Wiki
name: Haisaki Shinme
